title: Did the federal government cancel Nikki's $80 million contract?
subtitle: The junk news website said that the government cancelled a contract that wasn't with Nicky because the company decided that she hated America.
author: David Emery
vclaim: The U.S. government cancelled the $80 million contract with Nikki's makeup athlete, a company because "he hates America" and "he ignores dead veterans."
